{
  "info": {
    "name": "First Horizon - Unmasked Credit Card Accounts API",
    "description": "API collection for accessing unmasked credit card account numbers from Bottomline DBIQ. Demonstrates API-level bypass of UI masking for security/PCI compliance workflows.\n\nWorkflow: OAuth Authentication \u2192 Discover UserGroups \u2192 List Accounts \u2192 Search with Masking Control\n\n**Environment Variables Required:**\n- baseUrl: API base URL\n- client_id: OAuth client ID  \n- client_secret: OAuth client secret\n- scope: digital-banking\n- grant_type: client_credentials\n- sso_id: SSO identifier for HTTP_nameid header\n\n**Key Features:**\n- OAuth 2.0 client credentials flow with automatic token refresh\n- UserGroup discovery and account enumeration\n- Masked vs Unmasked account number demonstration\n- Proper field validation (USERGROUP, ACCOUNTNAME, ACCOUNTNUMBER, BANKCODE)",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "auth": {
    "type": "inherit"
  },
  "event": [
    {
      "listen": "prerequest",
      "script": {
        "type": "text/javascript",
        "exec": [
          "// Auto-acquire OAuth token before each request",
          "const tokenUrl = pm.environment.get('baseUrl') + '/oauth/v1/token';",
          "const clientId = pm.environment.get('client_id');",
          "const clientSecret = pm.environment.get('client_secret');",
          "const grantType = pm.environment.get('grant_type');",
          "const scope = pm.environment.get('scope');",
          "",
          "// Skip token refresh for OAuth endpoint itself",
          "if (pm.request.url.toString().includes('/oauth/v1/token')) {",
          "    return;",
          "}",
          "",
          "const tokenRequest = {",
          "    url: tokenUrl,",
          "    method: 'POST',",
          "    header: {",
          "        'Content-Type': 'application/x-www-form-urlencoded',",
          "        'Authorization': 'Basic ' + btoa(clientId + ':' + clientSecret)",
          "    },",
          "    body: {",
          "        mode: 'urlencoded',",
          "        urlencoded: [",
          "            { key: 'grant_type', value: grantType },",
          "            { key: 'scope', value: scope }",
          "        ]",
          "    }",
          "};",
          "",
          "pm.sendRequest(tokenRequest, (err, response) => {",
          "    if (err) {",
          "        console.log('Token request failed:', err);",
          "        return;",
          "    }",
          "    ",
          "    if (response.code === 200) {",
          "        const responseJson = response.json();",
          "        const accessToken = 'Bearer ' + responseJson.access_token;",
          "        pm.collectionVariables.set('access_token', accessToken);",
          "        console.log('Token refreshed successfully');",
          "    } else {",
          "        console.log('Token request failed with status:', response.code);",
          "        console.log('Response:', response.text());",
          "    }",
          "});"
        ]
      }
    }
  ],
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "access_token",
      "value": ""
    }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Authentication",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Get OAuth Token",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/x-www-form-urlencoded"
              }
            ],
            "auth": {
              "type": "basic",
              "basic": [
                {
                  "key": "username",
                  "value": "{{client_id}}"
                },
                {
                  "key": "password",
                  "value": "{{client_secret}}"
                }
              ]
            },
            "body": {
              "mode": "urlencoded",
              "urlencoded": [
                {
                  "key": "grant_type",
                  "value": "{{grant_type}}"
                },
                {
                  "key": "scope",
                  "value": "{{scope}}"
                }
              ]
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/oauth/v1/token",
              "host": [
                "{{baseUrl}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "oauth",
                "v1",
                "token"
              ]
            }
          },
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    const responseJson = pm.response.json();",
                  "    const accessToken = 'Bearer ' + responseJson.access_token;",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('access_token', accessToken);",
                  "    console.log('Access token set:', accessToken.substring(0, 20) + '...');",
                  "} else {",
                  "    console.log('OAuth failed with status:', pm.response.code);",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
